=== 外界反應、結果分析 ===
[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]的報導指出，人民民主黨是在選舉中意外取勝<ref name=AlJ1>{{cite news|title=Bhutan's opposition party scores upset win|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/07/2013713125727754144.html|accessdate=2013-07-15|newspaper=Al Jazeera|date=2013-07-13|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212214310/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/07/2013713125727754144.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

選舉結束後10天，當局將在「請願期」處理各項選舉投訴。之後<ref name=DNAIndia>{{cite web|title=Bhutan's Election Commission completes polls process, hands over MP list to King|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/world/1860978/report-bhutan-s-election-commission-completes-polls-process-hands-over-mp-list-to-king|work=DNA India|accessdate=2013-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720115640/http://www.dnaindia.com/world/1860978/report-bhutan-s-election-commission-completes-polls-process-hands-over-mp-list-to-king|archive-date=2013-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[策林·托傑|策林·托傑]]成為[[不丹總理|不丹總理]]，組建新政府<ref name=WashPost>{{cite news |title=Bhutan opposition party wins parliament election after calling for stronger ties with India |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/bhutan-opposition-party-wins-parliament-election-after-calling-for-stronger-ties-with-india/2013/07/14/d800c528-ec3b-11e2-818e-aa29e855f3ab_story.html |accessdate=2013-07-14 |newspaper=Washington Post |date=2013-07-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130716220449/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/bhutan-opposition-party-wins-parliament-election-after-calling-for-stronger-ties-with-india/2013/07/14/d800c528-ec3b-11e2-818e-aa29e855f3ab_story.html |archivedate=2013-07-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。取得國民議會席位的女性共有3名，當中人民民主黨的多爾吉·曲丹（Dorji Choden）後來成為不丹歷來首位女性大臣<ref name=DNAIndia/>。

[[印度總理|印度總理]][[曼莫漢·辛格|曼莫漢·辛格]]向勝選的人民民主黨表示祝賀，並保證印度會堅定地支持不丹<ref name="WashPost"/>。

